	<h1>Looking for rhpidfyre OS?</h1>
	<h2>rhpidfyre OS is a Linux distribution based on <a href="https://archlinux.org/" target="_blank">Arch Linux</a>, It is 'plug & play' with tweaks for performance & productivity.</h2>
	<i>- It's just a hobbyist distro I made for myself :).</i>
	<div>
		<Button
			text="Download"
			href="https://linux.rhpidfyre.io/download/"
			height="30px"
			background_color="hsl(0,0%,80%)"
			color="black"/>
		<Button
			text="Learn More"
			href="https://linux.rhpidfyre.io/"
			height="30px"
			background_color="transparent"
			color="var(--text-color)"/>
	</div>
